  lines:
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: Hmph.
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: "Don\u2019t take this as me being fine with you. "
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: 'Far from it. This is me simply sparing you because you interest me. '
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: However, I do not wish to lay my eyes on you again.
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: Goodbye.
    SpriteRange: 4
